{"tid":1767504,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[德國戰線］我哋要夠五萬個簽名！！！","createTime":"2019-12-03T10:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T10:23:01.000Z","uid":230840,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4960b9c13ab3e033ac1c429679d5d33b9c8abe","tid":1767504,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:52:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=155688099139149&amp;id=103890590985567\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D155688099139149%26id%3D103890590985567&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0Ksd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=430e55ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=155688099139149&amp;id=103890590985567</a><br />\n<br />\n話說德國有手足喺德國議會個官方website搞咗個聯署，要求德國政府正視香港人道問題，佢哋要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">喺聖誕節前集齊夠五萬個簽名</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家得返22日但都只係得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2500個左右</strong></span></span>嘅簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，求下咁多位手足簽過靚名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為簽名page係全德文，所以post Facebook 呢條link，有少少中英翻譯同簽名教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong> Freiheit f&uuml;r Hongkongers</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"50c6da4c86bc6069f665762be2e3ee8681aba6f6","tid":1767504,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:53:10.000Z","msg":"自推十連（1/10）"},{"pid":"a215517a6e40e525396f3b627b7702524ba6981a","tid":1767504,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:53:27.000Z","msg":"五大訴求缺一不可（2/10）"},{"pid":"01cbc6d1709f1c4ca961b7c002f3db4ac5b3e547","tid":1767504,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:53:44.000Z","msg":"解散警隊刻不容緩（3/10）"},{"pid":"48a4ba1784d3711358b3b85902cf0cd4a9233cba","tid":1767504,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:53:54.000Z","msg":"天滅中共（4/10）"},{"pid":"47cbb53e17c16da364edf15f04af90a252fe342f","tid":1767504,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:54:08.000Z","msg":"全黨死清光（5/10）"},{"pid":"d41f13005a5f9c9e63b1bd5a58fb87be1a24f4ed","tid":1767504,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:54:27.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家（6/10）"},{"pid":"3e6de51368c232ddc569c6084fce1b6adaa3c1f6","tid":1767504,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r8fEFzH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr8fEFzH.png&h=12796edd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果出呢個notification代表已經簽咗（7/10）"},{"pid":"ab05634a812a6c73c58137c7d30e11fed239857e","tid":1767504,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9992b06be75f7a93ba76afdc90e303232059a47a","tid":1767504,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:56:24.000Z","msg":"光復香港時代革命（8/10）"},{"pid":"a97c6097803d67cf466fe2f9126d7beb9d89a912","tid":1767504,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:57:01.000Z","msg":"by any means necessary (9/10)"},{"pid":"19327bb8e46102544b8486a72f9228e859ed7949","tid":1767504,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12